@'\" t
.\"     Title: XTest
.\"    Author: Kieron Drake
.\" Generator: DocBook XSL Stylesheets vsnapshot_9276 <http://docbook.sf.net/>
.\"      Date: <pubdate>6 June 2007</pubdate>
.\"    Manual: XTST FUNCTIONS
